{"tid":2138072,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【新解釋・三國志】貂蟬選角極創新　顛覆觀眾對三國固有認知","createTime":"2020-08-03T10:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T15:21:33.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"66094562e444108b6cfc64fc224ee75860d8bd0e","tid":2138072,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:59:18.000Z","msg":"如果講打機，日本版的三國誌相信陪伴不少香港人成長，想不到一套中國歷史，竟然由日本的遊戲公司做得比中國更好。除了遊戲，其實日本一直也對三個時期的歷史十分著迷，最近更開拍了新電影《新解釋・三國志》，演員陣容十分華麗！<br />\n<br />\n由EXILE成員岩田剛典擔任主角飾演趙雲，橋本環奈飾演黃夫人，山本美月扮小喬，大泉洋飾演劉備等等，反而最令人驚訝的是，貂蟬一改過往的形象，由大眾的靚女形象，變成「你絕對估唔到」！這部電影的編劇和導演都是福田雄一，是日本搞笑電影的代表，相信《新解釋・三國志》也會是搞笑向。"},{"pid":"cf9f8764a17dd774c27a2af245c8e9b6e808e113","tid":2138072,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:59:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200803/366962775706177536.jpeg/-VEzuwIxXnzvRc7erUT2Vxsug4uxsi7rVG50E1RudBM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200803%2F366962775706177536.jpeg%2F-VEzuwIxXnzvRc7erUT2Vxsug4uxsi7rVG50E1RudBM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=63ef3497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n橋本環奈飾演黃夫人，山本美月扮小喬"},{"pid":"0e380248bcc8ab88d09ef863f810da7972c0d20e","tid":2138072,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200803/366970241315639296.jpeg/KYhLMSbejzCGfAcj1B_7ddBDOK-t6vBM4E1bJOBNWyQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200803%2F366970241315639296.jpeg%2FKYhLMSbejzCGfAcj1B_7ddBDOK-t6vBM4E1bJOBNWyQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=24f73e50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200803/366970255056179200.jpeg/qVJLwQ53PgOoMCYZd_QN5cbr_2IzpXqz788G0u_PBtI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200803%2F36697025